 search algorithm, we can find high-performance architectures on\nNAS-Bench-101 and find a MobileNetV3 architecture that attains 79.2% top-1\naccuracy on ImageNet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Feb 2023 17:28:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-19"}
