ending disjoint rank one idempotents to disjoint idempotents\nalways assume the above form \\eqref{eq:standard} with $D_1=I_p$ and $D_2=I_q$,\nunless ${\\bf M}_n(\\mathbb{F}) = {\\bf M}_2(\\mathbb{Z}_2)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Feb 2023 06:28:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-23"}
