 regime, when the $\\alpha$ effect magnitude is near the instability\nthreshold, the interference of the dynamo modes of different spatial\nlocalization shows the Grand activity cycles of a period about 300 years.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Feb 2023 07:02:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 May 2023 03:05:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-17"}
