me were unknown or unmeasured and if secular time trends\noccurred. Therefore, including (time-varying) covariates describing the study\ncohort seems to be avoidable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Feb 2023 10:11:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-23"}
