ic participation to no dynamic\nparticipation, i.e., with every participant online. Consequently, this model\nprovides a foundation for analyzing dynamically available protocols.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Feb 2023 12:12:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 May 2023 10:29:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-04"}
